<body>  

    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-left">
            <span class="logo">🎓 University Feedback System</span>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-right">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/admin">🔒 Admin Login</a>
            <% if (user) { %>
            <a href="/vote">🗳️ Vote</a>
            <a href="/logout">🚪 Logout</a>
            <% } else { %>
            <a href="/login">Login</a>
            <a href="/register">Register</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </nav>

  
    <div class="topcontainer">
    <div class="leftside">
      <h1>Welcome to the University Feedback System</h1>
      <p>Give us your opinion on subjects and professors to help improve the university's education quality.</p>

      <% if (user) { %>
        <p>Logged in as <%= user %></p>
        <a href="/vote">Go to Voting</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <p>
          Already registered? <a href="/login">Login</a><br/>
          New user? <a href="/register">Register</a>
        </p>
      <% } %>
    <section class="importance-section">
        <h2>📢 Why This Feedback System Matters</h2>
        <p>The University Voting and Feedback System is designed to create a transparent, fair, and impactful way for students to express their academic experiences.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>🎓 Empower Students:</strong> Your voice matters. Share your experience with subjects and professors to help improve the university’s education quality.</li>
            <li><strong>📈 Improve Teaching Standards:</strong> Constructive feedback helps faculty understand what’s working and what isn’t — leading to better teaching methods and more engaging classes.</li>
            <li><strong>🧭 Guide Curriculum Design:</strong> Feedback and ratings help academic departments make informed decisions when it comes to revising syllabi, teaching strategies, or introducing new subjects.</li>
            <li><strong>🔐 Confidential & Secure:</strong> Your feedback is safely stored and only accessible to authorized admin personnel. You can be honest without fear — your privacy is respected.</li>
            <li><strong>🛠️ Continuous Improvement:</strong> The goal is not just evaluation, but evolution. Your opinions drive change, innovation, and overall improvement in university academics.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="importance-section">
      <h2>Guidelines</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Registration is MANDATORY</strong><br/>All students must register and log in to access the voting and feedback portal.</li>
        <li><strong>While registering, use your official name</strong><br/>Enter your full official name used in university records. This helps ensure authenticity and traceability.</li>
        <li><strong>Enter your own subjects and professors</strong><br/>Manually input the subjects you've studied and the names of the respective professors. Avoid fake entries.</li>
        <li><strong>One Submission Per User</strong><br/>Re-submissions will overwrite the previous one.</li>
        <li><strong>Be Honest and Constructive</strong><br/>Rate honestly and provide useful suggestions if needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Ratings Are Confidential</strong><br/>Responses are securely stored and only accessible to admins.</li>
        <li><strong>Avoid Offensive Language</strong><br/>Disrespectful language will result in disqualification.</li>
        <li><strong>Review Before Submitting</strong><br/>Once submitted, your feedback is final (unless editing is allowed).</li>
      </ol>
      </section>
    </div>

